{"tid":1591160,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇行街發夢人仕返工完全 focus 唔到，無曬上班熱情","createTime":"2019-09-24T04:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T16:52:21.000Z","uid":43327,"like":103,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"5c20215ce4805d4d8237b5bc4a0060712fc11c08","tid":1591160,"uid":43327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T04:48:42.000Z","msg":"細佬我就三十，每逢六日會去行街，幾個月前真係日日同老細通頂博盡，同年紀比算升得快<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但 612 港殤之後日日準時收工，反屋企就做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做到起貨同好攰先訓，日日訓得果 4-5 個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁岩 69 之前又屎忽痕轉左工（果行最大果幾間其中一間），71 果排日日釣魚，完全 focus 唔到，又試過食左 TG 又痾又嘔病假返唔到幾日工，最後做左兩個月到就比人炒埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過就唔洗日日對住果班「理性」藍絲，其實仲開心左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果果排就做左 1 個月全職文宣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢排又去左另一間新公司（果行最大果幾間另外一間），人工依舊，但以前覺得好輕鬆既工作今日完全 focus 唔到，做到亂曬。尋日見到 yellow object 又著左，嬲到一片空白。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 返工只係等收工做文宣。<br />\n<br />\n本來讀緊個 part time degree 返星期六日都掛住睇 live 完全聽唔入耳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我好擔心自己又會被炒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而再比炒 black list 既話，將來應該只能揀中資公司架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇同路人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 長痛不如短痛，我係咪應該辭職 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f04f679437489e0a1da80c7eb26aa8d9e4811b3e","tid":1591160,"uid":76058,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T04:54:57.000Z","msg":"三個月無返過工做野咁 一至五係office休息"},{"pid":"14b4bd446241399cf4b0f2227dfc562ae408a7e4","tid":1591160,"uid":78770,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T04:56:35.000Z","msg":"巴打自己會唔會有經濟負擔? 定係屋企唔洗你養你自己都有儲下錢可以應付到生活??<br />\n<br />\n辭唔辭工哩樣野 你自己決定<br />\n但如果你真係有經濟負擔 我唔建議你辭工 focus返係工作身上 抗爭運動係工餘時間做<br />\n如果你話我銀行入面嘅錢夠你生活用 咁你辭工同公司好來去去對雙方都係好事"},{"pid":"160af16c75c2d649e2330fa7b45904c43b299bc5","tid":1591160,"uid":63448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:02:17.000Z","msg":"Same 琴日做做下野睇完yellow object完全冇心機做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02cbc25211adb23ce03cee1c4a055f355a79bef6","tid":1591160,"uid":61105,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:05:01.000Z","msg":"番工先有錢捐比小朋友開飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9753abc3de08976a5255cc9ef916a8f811e8b9ad","tid":1591160,"uid":137604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:42:26.000Z","msg":"有同事逢星期一，二病假"},{"pid":"175b8423e5aaaddffb3c3e22023043c9ea157ea4","tid":1591160,"uid":244223,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:58:39.000Z","msg":"不嬲都冇熱情"},{"pid":"93d94dcf3f1b589da954024c085ab9c272ddb0a4","tid":1591160,"uid":310970,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:58:57.000Z","msg":"我都係，冇晒心情返工。雖然係咁，我都經常提自己，返工冇心機都好，都要最少交返d basic 貨出黎。 者係可能之前係130%, e+ 點都要交到100%. <br />\n<br />\n要間唔中放低電話，等自己可以focus 返工作上。<br />\n<br />\n但放左工，就真係冇晒心情娛樂。 以前打機 睇戲好快一日，e+ 就睇相關新聞，推twitter,出街。一諗起被捕手捉，真係做乜都唔會開心。。。"},{"pid":"c9c82522a9ef7cf6a7f9307f09c8f8346183ad4d","tid":1591160,"uid":228337,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:02:40.000Z","msg":"我由6月開始就係呢個狀態<br />\n好彩我嗰份係hea工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返緊工都上 Twitter 文宣"},{"pid":"75eb3db42f1114c619c5521553fe609edb562b71","tid":1591160,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:12:06.000Z","msg":"same, 要適時放鬆下"},{"pid":"d6ef04d0d6981e679e229596b8b00fb5c6b7a0e2","tid":1591160,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:13:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d384402296881d57258b29b6017563f1a6a6becd","tid":1591160,"uid":302618,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:32:00.000Z","msg":"我之前同巴打你一樣，搞到日常生活亂曬龍<br />\n<br />\n之後嘗試將每日嘅時間分區，幾點鐘至幾點返工，幾點至幾點睇新聞，咩鐘數留做自己想做嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n果個時間段就專心只係做果一樣嘢，唔掂電話電腦<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔介意，或者可以試試"},{"pid":"16b505a0ebead1384394fde18b77794285035caa","tid":1591160,"uid":121961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:50:42.000Z","msg":"要頂住呀"},{"pid":"49a2310a6ee9de3060adefbcbd8014f2d7392a5e","tid":1591160,"uid":24227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be7f7888faa5d0ecc562bd065be35bf59f49fb9","tid":1591160,"uid":115014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:22:28.000Z","msg":"日日番工都係諗公司幾時攬炒到執粒"},{"pid":"6dd0a0e3526c3757ae95745fe17b291063fec984","tid":1591160,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5be7f7888faa5d0ecc562bd065be35bf59f49fb9","tid":1591160,"uid":115014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:22:28.000Z","msg":"日日番工都係諗公司幾時攬炒到執粒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T10:13:05.000Z","msg":"same <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cdcef0dea2d7c550fe551b8782382567808e4e1","tid":1591160,"uid":43327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:01:09.000Z","msg":"仆街啦，返左成日工完全無 idea 自己做緊乜，只係不停將d file 搬來搬去又收工，完全 0 進度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前既我應該已經寫好 paper 執好 support 準備 reply<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e9cb3f71f8ba03cc7f2a1e0092489101d9f3b3","tid":1591160,"uid":43327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93d94dcf3f1b589da954024c085ab9c272ddb0a4","t